    }</style></noscript><div class="styles__Inner-sc-1zuwyu-1 vglK"><div class="styles__Content-sc-1zuwyu-2 kFsdQC"><h1 class="styles__Title-sc-1zuwyu-3 eaWGBG">Daniel Ross</h1><div class="styles__Subtitle-sc-1zuwyu-4 kTvdbB"><p>A London UK based <em>TypeScript/JavaScript/React Developer</em>, problem solver, and jack-of-all-trades.</p></div></div><a class="styles__ScrollAnchor-sc-1zuwyu-5 kccAkg fas fa-chevron-circle-down" href="#about"></a></div></section></div><div id="about" class="styles__Wrapper-sc-1t0x6lk-0 gwCscn"><section class="styles__Container-ojwgmk-0 dgtOEu"><div class="styles__Inner-ojwgmk-1 keQSBp"><div class="styles__Content-ojwgmk-3 bVYIJI"><h1 class="styles__Title-ojwgmk-2 keIAeg">About Me</h1><div class="styles__Text-ojwgmk-4 fGObrj"><p>I am an ex-academic, with a passion for JavaScript and a penchant for problem-solving, looking for  web development positions. I am interested in both front- and back-end JavaScript/TypeScript roles and am more than happy to learn any additional frameworks and libraries that may be required. If you are looking for help, or would just like a chat, please don&#x27;t hesitate to get in touch.</p></div></div></div></section></div><div id="skills" class="styles__Wrapper-sc-1t0x6lk-0 gwCscn"><section class="styles__Container-ojwgmk-0 cgyRxM inverted"><div class="styles__Inner-ojwgmk-1 keQSBp"><div class="styles__Content-ojwgmk-3 bVYIJI"><h1 class="styles__Title-ojwgmk-2 keIAeg">Skills</h1><div class="styles__Container-ven2in-0 iEZaqi"><div class="styles__ItemsContainer-ven2in-1 bTtoWE"><div title="HTML" class="styles__Item-ven2in-2 jNPlEq"><a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="styles__Anchor-ven2in-3 oOFaf"><div class="styles__Hexagon-ven2in-4 gWcLOP"><div class="styles__HexagonInner-ven2in-5 hVlnUE"><div class="styles__Logo-ven2in-6 itUxhg"><div><svg role="img" viewBox="0 0 24 24" xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"><title>HTML5 icon</title><path d="