-0 gwCscn"><section class="styles__Container-ojwgmk-0 dgtOEu inverted"><div class="styles__Inner-ojwgmk-1 keQSBp"><div class="styles__Content-ojwgmk-3 bVYIJI"><h1 class="styles__Title-ojwgmk-2 keIAeg"><a href="/projects">Featured Work</a></h1><div class="styles__Container-q020ub-0 gIPcLq"><article class="styles__Item-q020ub-17 bMDBrS"><div class="styles__Content-q020ub-3 hvdyjf"><p class="styles__Subtitle-q020ub-2 jESeDX">2021-11-18</p><div class="flex-container"><h1 class="styles__Title-q020ub-1 iOzCcQ"><a class="styles__StyledLink-q020ub-11 kOHmcO" href="/projects/social">Social</a></h1><div class="styles__Container-p0gjzx-0 flQPQx"><a href="https://social.rossdaniel.com" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="styles__Anchor-p0gjzx-1 iSVFaa"><i class="styles__Icon-p0gjzx-2 cJNSqb fas fa-globe fa-fw"></i></a><a href="https://github.com/notAlexRoss/social-media-app" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="styles__Anchor-p0gjzx-1 iSVFaa"><i class="styles__Icon-p0gjzx-2 cJNSqb fas fa-code-branch fa-fw"></i></a></div></div><div class="styles__Text-q020ub-13 dXNoyC"><p>A social media application, powered by Firebase, with Firebase Authentication, Cloud Firestore NoSQL database, and Cloud Storage. Apart from Firebase, the app consists of 100% client-side code, built upon rigorous database security rules that prevent direct-access attacks using otherwise public credentials. Built with TypeScript, React, and Tailwind CSS, it is fully responsive and highly accessible.</p></div><ul class="styles__Keywords-q020ub-14 gMCUNG"><li class="styles__Keyword-q020ub-15 dvWzLQ"><a href="https://www.typescriptlang.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="styles__KeywordInner-q020ub-16 eAFDJx">TypeScript</a></li><li class="styles__Keyword-q020ub-15 dvWzLQ"><a href="https://firebase.google.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="styles__KeywordInner-q020ub-16 eAFDJx">Firebase</a></li><li class="styles__Keyword-q020ub-15 dvWzLQ"><a href="https://tailwindcss.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="styles__KeywordInner-q020ub-16 eAFDJx">Tailwind</a></li><li class="styles__Keyword-q020ub-15 dvWzLQ"><a href="https://jestjs.io/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="styles__KeywordInner-q020ub-16 eAFDJx">Jest</a></li><li class="styles__Keyword-q020ub-15 dvWzLQ"><a href="https://reactjs.org/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="styles__KeywordInner-q020ub-16 eAFDJx">React</a></li><li class="styles__Keyword-q020ub-15 dvWzLQ"><a href="https://reactrouter.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="styles__KeywordInner-q020ub-16 eAFDJx">React Router</a></li><li class="styles__Keyword-q020ub-15 dvWzLQ"><a href="https://styled-components.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="styles__KeywordInner-q020ub-16 eAFDJx">Styled Components</a></li><li class="styles__Keyword-q020ub-15 dvWzLQ"><a href="https://www.javascript.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="styles__KeywordInner-q020ub-16 eAFDJx">JavaScript</a></li><li class="styles__Keyword-q020ub-15 dvWzLQ"><a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/HTML" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="styles__KeywordInner-q020ub-16 eAFDJx">HTML</a></li><li class="styles__Keyword-q020ub-15 dvWzLQ"><a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en-US/docs/Web/CSS" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="styles__KeywordInner-q020ub-16 eAFDJx">CSS</a></li></ul></div><a class="styles__Images-q020ub-4 gDNorp" href="/projects/social"><div class="styles__ImagesInner-q020ub-5 kaKgVW"><div class="styles__ImageDesktop-q020ub-10 gjWTwp gatsby-image-wrapper" style="position:relative;overflow:hidden"><div aria-hidden="true" style="width:100%;padding-bottom:56.25%"></div><img aria-hidden="true" src="data:image/png;base64," title="Social - Desktop" alt="Social - Desktop" style="position:absolute;top:0;left:0;width:100%;height:100%;object-fit:cover;object-position:center;opacity:1;transiti